Package: polarisability
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Baptiste", "Auguie",
    email = "baptiste.auguie@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
License: GPL-3 
Title: Polarisability of small particles for electromagnetic scattering
Description: The polarisability package provides a number of approximate formulas for the dipole, quadrupole, and octupole polarisability of small particles as described in the framework of the Rayleigh-Gans approximation of electromagnetic scattering.
Date: 2013-02-19
URL: https://github.com/baptiste/polarisability
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
BuildVignettes: true
Depends:
    dielectric,
    plyr,
    reshape2
Suggests:
    grid,
    ggplot2,
    testthat